graph TD

subgraph LEDHouseNotificationProcess

subgraph System
start_order_event((Order / Service Event Occurs))
gw_event_type{Event Type?}
task_detect_order_confirmed[Detect: Order Confirmed]
task_detect_order_delivered[Detect: Order Delivered]
task_detect_service_completed[Detect: Service Completed]
gw_merge_events{Merge Events}
task_generate_notification[Generate Notification Message]
gw_notification_method{Notification Method?}
task_send_email[Send Email Notification]
task_flag_manual_sms[Flag for Manual SMS / Call]
task_log_notification[Log Notification in System]
end_notification_logged((Notification Logged))
end

subgraph Customer
catch_receive_email((Receive Email Notification))
task_customer_views_notification[Customer Views Notification]
gw_customer_issue{Issue with Order?}
end_process_complete((Process Complete))
end

subgraph Admin
task_admin_receive_flag[Receive Manual SMS / Call Flag]
task_admin_contact_customer[Contact Customer - SMS / Call]
task_admin_mark_sent[Mark Notification as Sent]
end

end

subgraph Payment_Provider
task_pay_send_signal[Send Confirmation Signal to System]
end

start_order_event --> gw_event_type
gw_event_type --> task_detect_order_confirmed
gw_event_type --> task_detect_order_delivered
gw_event_type --> task_detect_service_completed

task_detect_order_confirmed --> gw_merge_events
task_detect_order_delivered --> gw_merge_events
task_detect_service_completed --> gw_merge_events

gw_merge_events --> task_generate_notification
task_generate_notification --> gw_notification_method

gw_notification_method --> task_send_email
gw_notification_method --> task_flag_manual_sms

task_send_email --> task_log_notification
task_log_notification --> end_notification_logged

task_send_email -.-> catch_receive_email
catch_receive_email --> task_customer_views_notification
task_customer_views_notification --> gw_customer_issue

gw_customer_issue --> end_process_complete
gw_customer_issue --> task_log_notification

task_flag_manual_sms --> task_admin_receive_flag
task_admin_receive_flag --> task_admin_contact_customer
task_admin_contact_customer --> task_admin_mark_sent
task_admin_mark_sent --> task_log_notification

task_pay_send_signal -.-> start_order_event